data.eml:eml: Leaf litter copepods from a cloud forest mountain top in Honduras (Copepoda: Cyclopidae, Canthocamptidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Fiers, Frank, Jocque, Merlijn (2013): Leaf litter copepods from a cloud forest mountain top in Honduras (Copepoda: Cyclopidae, Canthocamptidae). Zootaxa 3630 (2): 270-290, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3630.2.4
